# The review package intentionally includes the AutoCAD/ObjectARX runtime
# binaries needed to load the companion plug-in. Debug symbol files remain
# ignored because they are not required for reproduction and exceed GitHub's
# ordinary file-size limit.
!plugin/
!plugin/AutoCAD_2025_Debug_x64/
!plugin/AutoCAD_2025_Debug_x64/*.dll
!plugin/AutoCAD_2025_Debug_x64/*.arx
!plugin/AutoCAD_2025_Debug_x64/*.dbx
